              <td width="600" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p ALIGN="JUSTIFY"> <FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif">While Mallorca has the sun and the beaches, it also has over 2,000 years of history and culture to discover. Within these webpages you will find over 90 places to visit, each of them with their own story. You will also find an engaging history of this fascinating island complemented by stories on famous people, events, buildings and organisations. But it is not all about history and culture, there are also links to leisure parks for those who want to relax and links to activities for those who are feeling energetic. Hopefully, there is something here for everyone.</FONT></p>
